# Ble-RCU Daemon
This component is designed to provide a interface between bluez and the application for pairing, unpairing and voice commands handling.

# Getting Started
## Requirements
* CMake (>3.7)
* Qt (>5.4)
* libsystemd
* libdbus
* Bluez5


## Build
blercudaemon is a CMake project and can be built with the standard CMake workflow. To build, run the following commands.

cd ~/workspace/of/blercudaemon/repo
mkdir build && cd build

cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ../

make -j$(numproc)
sudo make install

